# WaveMeet iOS App Configuration

## Environment Variables

Create an `.env` file in the `ios/` directory with the following configuration:

```
# Backend API Configuration
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
REACT_APP_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:3001

# App Configuration
REACT_APP_ENV=development
REACT_APP_DEBUG=true
```

### For Device Testing

Update the IP address to match your Mac's IP:

```
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://192.168.x.x:3001
REACT_APP_SOCKET_URL=http://192.168.x.x:3001
```

Get your Mac's IP with: `ifconfig | grep "inet " | grep -v 127.0.0.1`
